snippet.title: Arena Breakout: Infinite Closed Beta Announcement Trailer | PC/Steam
snippet.description:
Attention soldiers! The battlefield comes to your home command center screens!  
Enlist for the Arena Breakout: Infinite PC/Steam Beta starting in Early May, Sign up NOW, and report for duty early at www.arenabreakoutinfinite.com.  
 
💰New Arena
- Uncompromised Immersion  
- Military Simulation  
- Tactical Extraction Shooter Looter  
 
#ArenaBreakoutPC #ArenaBreakoutInfinite #ABI
